      "role": "user",
      "content": "sometimes i sit here and i just look at my hands and i dont even recognize them. it feels like the person who actually lived, the one with the dreams and the spark, died a long time ago. i'm just... i'm just the leftovers. a walking corpse going through the motions while the real me is already gone.",
